      "body" : "I tried the full command and I got <code>[ERROR] Unknown lifecycle phase &quot;.mainClass=com.example.Main&quot;. You must specify a valid lifecycle phase or a goal</code>. Not sure if it&#39;s because of Windows. But I fixed it by adding <code>&lt;properties&gt;&lt;exec.mainClass&gt;</code> in <code>pom.xml</code> and running just <code>mvn exec:java</code>. I suppose I could also add <code>&lt;exec.args&gt;</code> for arguments. Tedious though."
