  "title" : "run main class of Maven project",
  "body" : "<p>I've created a simple console Java application that is built with Maven. Is there a way that the main class (which doesn't require any arguments) can be run from the command-line using a maven command like:</p>\n\n<pre><code>mvn run-app com.example.MainClass\n</code></pre>\n"
